flowchart TD
    A[Start]
    B[Entity Loaded into Persistence Context]
    B@{ shape: comment, label: "em.find() or em.persist()" }
    A --> B

    C[Entity is Managed]
    B --> C

    D[Evict/Detach Entity]
    D@{ shape: comment, label: "em.detach(entity)" }
    C --> D

    E[Entity is Detached]
    E@{ shape: comment, label: "No longer tracked by persistence context" }
    D --> E

    F[Further Changes Not Tracked]
    F@{ shape: comment, label: "Modifications are not persisted" }
    E --> F

    G[Optionally Reattach Entity]
    G@{ shape: comment, label: "em.merge(entity) to reattach" }
    F --> G

    H[Entity is Managed Again]
    G --> H
